## Supabase Clients

| Client | File | Use For |
|---|---|---|
| Server (cookie-based) | `lib/supabase-server.ts` | Server Components, Route Handlers |
| Admin (service role) | `lib/supabase-admin.ts` | Bypasses RLS — admin & cron only |
| Browser | `lib/supabase/client.ts` | Client Components only |

## Migration Rules
- File naming: `YYYYMMDDNNNN_description.sql`
- All migrations must be idempotent where possible (`CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS`, etc.)
- Always add RLS policies for new tables with user data
- Test migrations in Supabase dashboard before deploying

## Enum Definitions
See `lib/db-enums.ts` for TypeScript enum definitions matching database enums.
